rows.label: tlk43400541_02_msg0001
rows.name:
As you can see, Invidia is
a land filled with plenty
of water and greenery.

rows.label: tlk43400541_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Thanks to this, we also have
plenty of food. We will not be
beaten by any other country.

rows.label: tlk43400541_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Even if we were to get into
a war with Superbia, we would
not struggle for food.

rows.label: tlk43400541_02_msg0004
rows.name:
If it became a war of
attrition, without doubt,
victory would be Invidia's.

rows.label: tlk43400541_02_msg0005
rows.name:
It's only right the military continues
to regulate the Folta rations.
